разрешила войти. И отключила главный инструмент.\n\nКто зайдёт и останется: выиграет не плейбуком. Сервисом.\n\n@vipcare_io", "image_html": null}], "linkedin_post": {"text": "LINKEDIN POST:\n\nFinland just opened Europe's newest iGaming market and banned VIP programs before anyone could use them.\n\nStarting July 2027, Finland ends its state gambling monopoly. Entain, Flutter, Betsson, Kindred, and LeoVegas are among the 24 operators already in the license queue. The market generates an estimated €1.9B in annual GGR.\n\nBut the law is explicit: tiered VIP programs, volume-based loyalty schemes, and player incentives tied to activity are all prohibited. All bonuses must be offered on equal terms to every player, wagering requirements capped at 5x. No rakeback, no tier acceleration, no personalised treatment for high-value depositors.\n\nFor VIP teams, this is a real test. The toolkit built over years cannot be deployed: no segmentation-based bonuses, no escalating rewards, no personalised incentives for big players. What remains is service quality, payment speed, and product experience.\n\nThe operators who will win in Finland are the ones genuinely good at VIP management, not just good at giving money away.\n\nMost haven't had to find out the difference. Yet.\n\n#iGaming #VIPRetention #CasinoOperations #PlayerExperience"}}